 /** @namespace EAM **/
 
 /**
 * Engagement Analytics Model
 * @class
 * @memberof EAM
 */
function Eam(global){
 
	/**
	* @typedef {Number} Time Time in seconds.
	* @memberof EAM
	*/
 
	/** @const */	
	this.global = global;
 
	/** @const */	
	this.none = undefined;
 
	this.history = [];
 
 
	/** Get current time.
     * @returns {Number} Time in seconds.
     */	
	this.time = function(){
		var now = new Date();
		return now.getTime();
	}
 
	/** Get current time.
	 * @param {Object} result
	 * @param {String} key
	 * @param {String} values
     * @returns {(Object|Undefined)} result
     */	
	this.getWhenAny = function(result, key, values){
		var items = values.split(',');
		for(var i=items.length;i--;){
			if(items[i] == key) return result;
		}
	}
 
	this.listen = function(context, events, listeners){
		var $context = this.$(context),
			names = events.split(',');
 
		for(var i=0; i<names.length; i++){
 
			function notifyListeners(event){
				var index = listeners.length;
				while(index>0){
					var listener = listeners[--index];
					listener(event);
				}
			}
 
			$context.bind(names[i], notifyListeners);	
		}
	}
 
}
 
module.exports = Eam;
